Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 07 of Hip MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Musculature' from the dropdown menu

When I select 'Further findings' radio button
Then 'Edema-like signal intensity' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fatty degeneration' checkbox is enabled
And 'Muscular atrophy' checkbox is enabled
And 'Apophysitis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fascial tear' checkbox is enabled
And 'Reduced ischiofemoral distance' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Edema-like signal intensity' checkbox
Then 'Epimyseal/peripheral' radio button is enabled
And 'Myotendinous/central' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Muscular atrophy' checkbox
Then 'Moderate' radio button is enabled
And 'Advanced' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Fascial tear' checkbox
And 'Muscle herniation' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Reduced ischiofemoral distance' checkbox
Then 'Minimum distance' input field is enabled
